---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Nachiket Kulkarni"
  description="About Nachiket Kulkarni — Senior DevOps / Platform Engineer with 8+ years of experience in cloud infrastructure, MLOps, and developer platforms."
>
  <div class="page">
    <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Senior DevOps / Platform Engineer · Pune, India</p>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm a Senior Software Engineer in DevOps at <strong>Autodesk</strong>, where I build and maintain
        cloud infrastructure and MLOps pipelines for enterprise clients including <strong>Pixar</strong>,
        <strong>Hyundai</strong>, and <strong>L&T</strong>. With 8+ years in the industry, I specialize in
        bridging the gap between software engineering and infrastructure, enabling teams to ship faster and
        more reliably.
      </p>

      <p>
        My experience spans leading DevOps transformations — from containerization and Kubernetes adoption
        to full GitOps workflows with ArgoCD and Kyverno policy enforcement. Before Autodesk, I built
        CI/CD pipelines and cloud automation at <strong>NICE</strong>, contributed to platform engineering
        at <strong>Coupa Software</strong>, and honed my quality engineering skills at <strong>TIBCO Software</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        I hold a <strong>Master of Science in Computer Science from Georgia Tech</strong>, with coursework
        focused on cloud computing, distributed systems, and machine learning. This academic foundation
        complements my hands-on experience in deploying AI/ML workloads in production, building scalable
        data platforms, and designing infrastructure for high-availability systems.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm passionate about automation, infrastructure as code, GitOps, and building developer
        platforms that improve engineering velocity. When I'm not working on cloud infrastructure, I enjoy
        exploring agentic AI tooling, contributing to open-source projects, and writing about DevOps
        patterns and platform engineering practices.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="skills">
      <h2>Core Skills</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3>Cloud & Infrastructure</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">AWS</span>
            <span class="tag">GCP</span>
            <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
            <span class="tag">Helm</span>
            <span class="tag">Terraform</span>
            <span class="tag">Pulumi</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3>CI/CD & GitOps</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">ArgoCD</span>
            <span class="tag">GitHub Actions</span>
            <span class="tag">Jenkins</span>
            <span class="tag">Kyverno</span>
            <span class="tag">Flux</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3>MLOps & Data</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">MLflow</span>
            <span class="tag">Kubeflow</span>
            <span class="tag">Airflow</span>
            <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
            <span class="tag">Streamlit</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3>Languages</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Python</span>
            <span class="tag">Bash</span>
            <span class="tag">Go</span>
            <span class="tag">YAML</span>
            <span class="tag">HCL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent-light);
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-group h3 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    color: var(--accent-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
</style>
